        IrisDataSetIterator handles traversing through the Iris Data Set.
        See Also:
        https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Iris Typical usage of an iterator is akin to: DataSetIterator iter = ..; while(iter.hasNext()) { DataSet d = iter.next(); //iterate network... } For custom numbers of examples/batch sizes you can call: iter.next(num) where num is the number of examples to fetch
